    </author>
    <date day="12" month="May" year="2015"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>Point to multipoint (P2MP) BFD is designed to verify multipoint
   connectivity.  This document specifies the support of P2MP BFD in
   TRILL.  Similar to TRILL point-to-point BFD, BFD Control packets in
   TRILL P2MP BFD are transmitted using an RBridge Channel.</t>
    </abstract>
  </front>
